snippet.title: Gregor Soundhome
snippet.description:
Gregors Soundhome is a channel that specializes in an oldschool deep house, minimal dNb and techno sound. All mixes are created in my music room on a classic deck by myself.
I hope you enjoy it, and I'm happy to share the muzik I love with you by puttin' it into a mix.
I also create a hardware setup for making own tracks or jam sessions. 


THANKS FOR LISTENING ! :-)
LOVE 💚

Gregor✌️
